RTCagent packaging examples
===========================

Starter files for deb/rpm packages built with nfpm (`rtcagent.yaml`,
`rtcagent_workflow.yaml`).

- `rtcagent.service` — systemd unit (paths under `/usr/local/rtcagent`).
- `rtcagent.init` — SysV init script for non-systemd hosts.
- `rtcagent.env.example` — copy to `/usr/local/rtcagent/etc/rtcagent.env` and
  adjust HEP collector + application paths before enabling the service.

Requires Linux with eBPF (BTF), CAP_BPF / privileged mode, and a supported
application binary (kamailio, opensips, freeswitch, rtpengine).
